{"tid":147111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當更警又拎1分！ 旺角當更警唔見車匙","createTime":"2017-03-07T15:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T15:34:48.000Z","uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72d432c5c8463cafa3cdd7cacdaa60a837c4b904","tid":147111,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"當更警車車長遺失車匙　警方籲市民拾獲交回<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/76394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F76394&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=59f5fded\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/76394</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/458062/xlarge/8f11a4708496cc99a2caa4e3ccc2d2f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F458062%2Fxlarge%2F8f11a4708496cc99a2caa4e3ccc2d2f8.jpg&h=67da7afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼早前有警員遺失警用手機後，今再有警車車長執勤期間遺失車匙！一名隸屬旺角警區的警員於今午（7日）在旺角欅樹街執行職務期間，發現遺失身上的警車車匙，警方其後立即展開調查及搜尋，惟暫未有發現，案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由旺角警區跟進調查，呼籲市民如拾獲該警車車匙，應立即致電999，並把該警車車匙交到就近的警署，或致電3661　8646與調查人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，就裝備的保管及使用有嚴格的規定，已就有關事件展開內部調查，如發現有人員違規，定會嚴肅處理。"},{"pid":"04c3ff6865c11c11bcc6fccaede69a44cd26b809","tid":147111,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"幾時唔見埋支槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}